{"tid":1793759,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港獨立】的三大原因","createTime":"2019-12-22T15:21:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T15:55:07.000Z","uid":322120,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2c25ee89f97e7c2875952c57efd2c565c0a2dbba","tid":1793759,"uid":322120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T15:21:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">其實我一直認為「獨立」係香港人嘅唯一結局。<br />\n原因有三:</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(一):我哋其實就好似一個沉完咸水翻嚟個封建嘅大家庭住嘅仔&hellip;&hellip;結果係呢個「番書仔」一定係老豆眼中好唔順眼!(因此成日揾特務昅住我哋)</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">(二):個仔有自己經濟能力、係唔會鍾意同屋企人住。仲要個衰老豆管哩管嚕、最近仲夠pop埋家暴！<br />\n想個仔唔搬出嚟住、都幾難！</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">(三):個仔一直有錢過老豆、最近仲發現佢周身街數，又不擅理財(攪埋啲國進民退)。<br />\n呢劑真係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔離家出走都唔掂！！！</span></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b06da3851024487ad9dd6284ff68693ecbef003","tid":1793759,"uid":13173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T15:24:26.000Z","msg":"其實都唔算係老豆，而只不過係無啦啦有日喺街到有個陌生人過嚟認做你老豆，話自古以嚟係佢個仔乜乜物物"},{"pid":"9b0329c230dbee67e4efb959546f59b987b90ed7","tid":1793759,"uid":310883,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T15:26:27.000Z","msg":"香港人以家連街頭抗爭都放棄埋 仲話要獨立？<br />\n搞笑咩"},{"pid":"e9a151e87c53cf5338e73fb55ee48c77bb90e328","tid":1793759,"uid":322120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b06da3851024487ad9dd6284ff68693ecbef003","tid":1793759,"uid":13173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"